{% doc %}
  @prompt
    You are a senior Shopify OS 2.0 theme developer.
    Using the attached reference screenshot, create a custom Shopify section called “Frequently Asked Questions” that matches the layout, style, and interaction exactly.
    
    Section Header:
    
    Centered heading text:
    
    “Frequently Asked Questions”
    
    Subtitle text below heading:
    
    “Find answers to common questions about shipping, returns, sizing, and more. Need help? Contact our support team anytime.”
    
    Clean spacing between heading and content
    
    FAQ Item Design:
    
    Each FAQ item should include:
    
    A rounded container/card
    
    A numbered circle on the left (1, 2, 3…)
    
    Question text next to the number
    
    A chevron arrow icon on the right
    
    Answer text revealed when expanded
    
    Accordion Behavior:
    
    Clicking the question toggles open/close
    
    Smooth height animation
    
    Only one item open at a time (accordion behavior)
    
    Chevron rotates when active
    
    Design Requirements:
    
    Light gray background for question row
    
    White background for section
    
    Rounded corners
    
    Subtle shadow or divider
    
    Clean, modern UI (Dawn / modern ecommerce style)
    
    Shopify Section Requirements:
    
    Use Liquid + JSON schema
    
    Use repeatable blocks for FAQ items
    
    Each block must allow:
    
    Question text
    
    Answer (rich text)
    
    Section settings should include:
    
    Heading text
    
    Subtitle text
    
    Top & bottom padding
    
    Accessibility:
    
    Keyboard accessible
    
    ARIA attributes for accordion
    
    Proper semantic markup
    
    Code Output Rules:
    
    Provide complete Shopify section code
    
    Include:
    
    HTML (Liquid)
    
    CSS inside {% style %} tags
    
    JavaScript inside {% javascript %} tags
    
    JSON schema
    
    Code must be copy-paste ready
    
    Follow Shopify OS 2.0 best practices
    
